# root-pin — opt this repo into the global root-main hooks.
#
# Presence of this file (tracked, in the root checkout) arms two global
# Claude Code hooks deployed from ~/.claude/:
#
#   guard-root-branch.sh — denies `git switch` / `git checkout <branch>`
#                          in the root checkout (the first `git worktree
#                          list` entry); linked worktrees are unaffected.
#   sync-root-main.sh    — fast-forwards the root's `main` at session
#                          start and after a `gh pr merge`.
#
# The file's contents are not parsed — only its presence matters.
# Hook source lives in the dotfiles repo (dot_claude/). See CLAUDE.md,
# "Branching & worktrees".
